OL,3,CMan jailed for laser attacks on
OL,4,Caircraft
OL,6,FA Somerset man has been jailed for two
OL,7,Fcounts of directing a laser beam at
OL,8,Faircraft - including targeting a plane
OL,9,Fwith hundreds of passengers.
OL,11,FAndrew Wilson, 53 and from Martock,
OL,12,Fwas sentenced to four months
OL,13,Fimprisonment at Taunton Crown Court on
OL,14,FThursday 11 April.
OL,16,FAt an earlier hearing he had admitted
OL,17,Fto directing a laser beam at aircraft
OL,18,Fon two occasions - an offence under
OL,19,Fthe Laser Misuse Act 2018.
