OL,6,FThe first incident happened around
OL,7,F11.20pm on Thursday 3 August 2022, he
OL,8,Ftargeted a helicopter flying over
OL,9,FYeovil.
OL,11,FOn the second occasion, at about
OL,12,F11.55pm on Monday 14 August, he shone
OL,13,Fthe laser at an Airbus A320 passenger
OL,14,Fplane flying over Yeovil on its
OL,15,Fdescent to Bristol Airport, with
OL,16,Falmost 200 people on board.
OL,18,FBoth aircraft were able to make a safe
OL,19,Flanding.
