OL,4,Caircraft
OL,6,FThey also said attacks like this can
OL,7,Flead to retina damage and long-term
OL,8,Fdegradation of eyesight which could
OL,9,Fcost a pilot their career.
OL,11,FPC Jason Marshalsea, who worked on the
OL,12,Fcase, said: "Shining a laser beam at
OL,13,Fan aircraft is dangerous and
OL,14,Firresponsible and could result in
OL,15,Fcatastrophic consequences.
OL,17,F"Wilson not only jeopardised the
OL,18,Feyesight of several pilots, but he
OL,19,Falso unnecessarily and recklessly
OL,20,Fendangered the lives of hundreds of
OL,21,Finnocent people on those aircraft."
